exitdata.feedback:
The instructions were a little wordy for my taste. I found myself both feeling like I had been given too much to take in, and that I understood the important concepts regardless. 

It is inconsistent which screens require that you need to click Next to proceed from, and which will be advanced automatically when you click "Submit". Also, I think it's slightly unclear that choosing between the two games is labeled as its own "Round."

All in all though this was great and the interface is really nice.
